{"tid":726016,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook 準備購買英超播放權","createTime":"2018-07-02T05:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:23:57.000Z","uid":19889,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c010da1ad23aedefe74c81b7567876837311a534","tid":726016,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:26:47.000Z","msg":"Facebook 除了是社交平台，近年亦加入了影片播放和直播元素，之前我們報導過 Facebook 直播 MLS 美職聯的比賽，有關這社交平台進軍大型運動賽事直播行列亦時有所聞，最近有報導指 Facebook 正在洽談一宗重大的交易，涉及的是全球有不少粉絲的英格蘭超級聯賽的播放權。<br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社指 Facebook 即在洽談東南亞地區的英超播放權，讓他們可以在泰國、老撾、柬埔寨和越南播放英超球賽，Facebook 預期在未來數星期就會作出公佈。而因應對手冰島的平均高度比阿根廷高6厘米，所以特意安排1米83的奧達文迪及1米87的馬高斯盧祖出任中堅，而馬斯真蘭奴將會返回老本行防中位置。報導指 Facebook 將會取得 3 年的獨家網絡播放權，他們希望因此吸引更多人使用和花時間在 Facebook 之上。不過能夠在該地區播放英超全數 380 場賽事的還有電視網絡 BeIN Sports，有指他們以 2.5 億美元取得了東南亞地區的 3 年播放權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www4.pictures.zimbio.com/gi/Nicolas+Otamendi+Roberto+Firmino+Liverpool+n9ZYt37s6k8l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww4.pictures.zimbio.com%2Fgi%2FNicolas%2BOtamendi%2BRoberto%2BFirmino%2BLiverpool%2Bn9ZYt37s6k8l.jpg&h=11c37a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/02/facebook-looking-to-acquire-english-premier-league-broadcast-rights/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2Ffacebook-looking-to-acquire-english-premier-league-broadcast-rights%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=uLK1R3VyKD4%2BN24X34HBUvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=74000478\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/02/facebook-looking-to-acquire-english-premier-league-broadcast-rights/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"aac63909fe678178fdc66d2f529bde52d9a20836","tid":726016,"uid":33408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"而因應對手冰島的平均高度比阿根廷高6厘米，所以特意安排1米83的奧達文迪及1米87的馬高斯盧祖出任中堅，而馬斯真蘭奴將會返回老本行防中位置。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷球員都係屎來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im